  "_comment": "MaineCare Benefits Manual = Maine's Medicaid rules (10-144 CMR Ch.101). Single flat SOS index page; Ch.II = service-specific coverage policy, Ch.III = reimbursement allowances. All docs are DOCX (a few legacy .doc) — fetch-reference state-policy handler will need docx→txt (pandoc/textutil), not pdftotext. Filenames are revision-stamped (e.g. 'LUP 04.05.2015', '2026-093 RPR') so URLs change on amendment; two storage paths in use: /inline-files/ (newer) and /content/assets/ (older). Ch.III §113 Transportation absorbed into Ch.II §113.",
